page.title: 02CAMBUSNETHAN & NEWMAINS II
page.content:
Since 1914 there have been several phases of housing development:- 1. 1919 to 1939 Semi-villas, four in a block with gardens{(GR. 802554, {805559, 823562, 826564)} 2. 1945 to 1960 Semi-villas, four in a block with gardens{(GR. 804563, {808556, 804553, 823566) { }3. 1960 to 1975 Private and Local Authority. Private bungalows (GR. 803 558, 835568), Semi-villa (GR. 805555). Local Auth. terraced (GR. 812556) and flats (GR. 818568) 4. 1975 to 1985 Mostly Private Semi-villas, Villas and Bungalows{(GR. {813561, 812554)
N.B. Developments{CENTRED}on the grid references stated above.
